wikipedia_page.main: Harry Darby (born 1902, date of death unknown) was a British wrestler. He competed in the freestyle bantamweight event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. Darby was also the British bantamweight champion in 1925.

response: Harry Darby (January 23, 1895January 17, 1987) was an American politician from Kansas.
Interstate 635 (Kansas–Missouri) is named the Harry Darby Memorial Highway for him in both Kansas and Missouri.
*Finding aid for Harry Darby Oral History, Dwight D. Eisenhower Presidential Library
